OL,3,CDoctors call for 'bold actions' to
OL,4,Ctackle 'vaping epidemic'
OL,6,FTop doctors have called for
OL,7,Flegislation aimed at tackling youth
OL,8,Fvaping to include a total ban on
OL,9,Fdisposable e-cigarettes and all
OL,10,Fflavours apart from tobacco.
OL,12,FThe British Medical Association (BMA)
OL,13,Fhas urged ministers to "take bold and
OL,14,Fbrave actions" to protect the health
OL,15,Fof children and young people amid a
OL,16,F"vaping epidemic".
