OL,3,CDoctors call for 'bold actions' to
OL,4,Ctackle 'vaping epidemic'
OL,6,FDr Penelope Toff, chair of the BMA's
OL,7,Fpublic health medicine committee,
OL,8,Fcalled on the current government "to
OL,9,Fgo even further" than the plans
OL,10,Foutlined by Mr Sunak.
OL,12,FShe described the BMA report - Taking
OL,13,Four breath away: why we need stronger
OL,14,Fregulation of vapes - as a "blueprint"
OL,15,Fof the actions that should be taken by
OL,16,Fministers.
OL,18,FThe report calls for a ban on the sale
OL,19,Fof disposable vapes which would cause
OL,20,Fboth harm to children and to the
OL,21,Fenvironment.
