OL,3,CDoctors call for 'bold actions' to
OL,4,Ctackle 'vaping epidemic'
OL,6,FThe BMA also suggests all vape
OL,7,Fflavours apart from tobacco should be
OL,8,Fbanned, with measures introduced to
OL,9,Fprohibit the use of imagery, colouring
OL,10,Fand branding on packaging and e-
OL,11,Fcigarettes, as well as further
OL,12,Frestrictions on all advertising and
OL,13,Fmarketing.
OL,15,FDr Toff warned e-cigarette use among
OL,16,Fyoungsters is a "serious public health
OL,17,Fthreat", adding: "We are calling on
OL,18,Fministers to take bold and brave
OL,19,Factions that will make a real
OL,20,Fdifference."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
