OL,3,CDoctors call for 'bold actions' to
OL,4,Ctackle 'vaping epidemic'
OL,6,FShe added: "While this government has
OL,7,Frightly pledged to tackle smoking and
OL,8,Fvaping, the test will be in how it
OL,9,Facts."
OL,11,FPublication of the BMA's report comes
OL,12,Fafter analysis by public health
OL,13,Fcharity Action on Smoking and Health
OL,14,F(Ash) found 11% of the adult
OL,15,Fpopulation in Britain vape - the
OL,16,Fequivalent of 5.6 million people.
