OL,4,Ctackle 'vaping epidemic'
OL,6,FThe figure is the highest since Ash
OL,7,Fstarted asking about vaping in its
OL,8,FSmokefree GB analysis in 2017.
OL,10,FA separate report by Ash also
OL,11,Festimated 18% of 11 to 17-year-olds in
OL,12,FBritain - or around 980,000 youngsters
OL,13,F- have vaped in 2024.
OL,15,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,16,Fspokesperson said: "The marketing of
OL,17,Fvapes to children and young people is
OL,18,Futterly unacceptable.
