OL,3,CDoctors call for 'bold actions' to
OL,4,Ctackle 'vaping epidemic'
OL,6,F"Vapes can be an effective way for
OL,7,Fadult smokers to quit, but we have
OL,8,Falways been clear that children and
OL,9,Fadult non-smokers should never vape.
OL,11,F"The Tobacco and Vapes Bill will stop
OL,12,Fvapes from deliberately being branded
OL,13,Fand advertised to appeal to children,
OL,14,Fincluding by regulating flavours,
OL,15,Fpackaging, and changing how and where
OL,16,Fthey are displayed in shops."
